Class Path

java.lang.Object
  location.Path
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Path>
public class Path
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Path>, java.io.Serializable

This Creates a Path which represents a Part of the route taken on the trip it will take the distance between the two points and the time difference and work out the average speed and define what possible categories it falls in.

Author:
Matthew Schmidt
